metadata.name: 27Delly - Bonita (Official Music Video)
metadata.description:
Bonita Apple BOMB Video! "Bonita" official music video has arrived. 27Delly x Glass partnered with Telfar, 1800Tequila & VFILES to throw Harlem's first Women's Herstory Month Brownstone Party! Tons of NY's finest tastemakers, socialites, artists, leaders etc., were in attendance and it was a vibe!

We're bringing that vibe directly to your screens!

Portion of Proceeds will be donated to Juneteenth4EVA an annual event in Harlem to celebrate the liberation of slavery in 1866!

Enjoy!
